name: Finn 'the Human' Mertens
bio: Adventurer and hero, last human, defender of good

name: Bonnibel Bubblegum
bio: Scientist, bearer of candy power, ruler of the candy kingdom

name: Jake the ranger.
bio: Former criminal, then ranger, now nerd. Enjoys women and rocks.

name: Dakota the nerd.
bio: Dakota is a nerd who does nerd things all day, and he loves it!

name: Freddy the fisherman
bio: Freddy, once a hardened baddass is now a fisherman who enjoys capturing fish in his net and eating them alive.
